title: Go Epic with Thule - Thule Adventure Team
description:
Show us your passion for multisport and you have the chance to win a trip to hang out with Thule Adventure Team, one of the world's best adventure racing teams! 

Upload your best video now and join the competition!
www.epicthule.com

The competition runs from September 30 to December 9, 2013.
_______________


The Thule Adventure Team is one of the world's best adventure racing teams, consisting of 5 athletes who compete in the toughest Adventure races in the world. The team headed by Martin Flinta includes Per Vestling, and Eva Nyström from Sweden, Myriam "Mimi" Guillot and Jacky Boisset from France, and Marcel Hagener from Germany.

Learn more about Thule Adventure Team:
http://www.thule.com/thulecrew
